metadata.name: Narcissus Narcosis
metadata.description:
Hipparcos, genius hacker of Megalopolis, is immersed via a D-Streamâ„¢ interface in a Liminal Space of a Historical Simulation.  
This space is an ephemeral place where Hipparcos must solve all CO/DEC issues related to the recompilation of pieces of memory from a large database accumulated over centuries.  
In addition to the sedimented bits of code that she must get rid of, she must also draw on her knowledge of the era on which she is working to restore an acceptable degree of reality so that it is validated as a simulated reality within the Simulation.  
Hipparcos is experienced in this kind of work and the dangers inherent in diving in deep areas such as Narcissus Narcosis, which makes her one of the best in her field.

Narcissus Narcosis  
[45s / 4K / 280MB]  
Benjamin Bardou
